# Template for tests/fixtures/lab_real_groundtruth.yaml — A10 acceptance gate.
#
# After the manual lab capture session (decisions.md D8/D9):
#   1. Drop tests/fixtures/lab_real.usdz from the iPad RoomPlan/Polycam scan.
#   2. Tape-measure each speaker's az/el/dist relative to the listener centroid
#      and each room corner's (x, z) in the same listener-frame.
#   3. Copy this file to lab_real_groundtruth.yaml (drop the .template suffix).
#   4. Replace every TODO value with the measured value.
#   5. Run `pytest -m lab tests/test_acceptance_lab_room.py`.
#
# Field set consumed by tests/test_acceptance_lab_room.py — keep keys/types as-is:
#   speakers[i].channel  (int, 1..N monotonic)
#   speakers[i].az_deg   (float, degrees, listener-frame)
#   speakers[i].el_deg   (float, degrees, listener-frame; +up)
#   speakers[i].dist_m   (float, metres, listener-frame radial)
#   room.corner_positions[i].x  (float, metres, listener-frame)
#   room.corner_positions[i].z  (float, metres, listener-frame)
#
# Tolerances enforced by the acceptance test (decisions.md D8):
#   * az_deg:    ±5° per speaker
#   * dist_m:    ±0.10 m per speaker
#   * corner:    <0.10 m per corner (Euclidean in xz)

